MuSigPro is the world's first AI singing quality judge. Try it out now, for free!

MuSigPro is a karaoke app which the feature is different and never found in any similar app such as Smule, WeSing, StarMaker, etc. This app focuses on the singing competition and a place for the user to practice and improve their singing capability to get better quality.
This app also allows you, the brand owner, to conduct singing competitions for your customers. Singing competition could easily increase your brand engagement as singing is everyone’s favorite thing to do, this can not be done by the other apps such as Smule, WeSing, StarMaker, etc.
So, here we go, if you still think this app is similar to Smule, WeSing, StarMaker, etc, download and find the great and the differences by your own self!
